dct_description_sm: Inset maps of Liberia, Nile River, Cape Colony, Cape Verde Islands and St. Helena.
From: Johnson's new illustrated family atlas.
"Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1864 by A.J. Johnson, in the Clerks Office of the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York."
